ound information and identifying the many references to Fichte.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aPhilosophy of nature. 0aPhilosophy, Germany19th century. 4aPhilosophy : Continental Philosophy. 4aPhilosophy : German Idealism. 4aPhilosophy : History of Philosophy. 4aPhilosophy : Philosophy. 7aPHILOSOPHY / General.2bisacsh1 aSnow, Dale E., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143846865540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438468655423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438468655/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles